    {
      "para_id": "Q001717.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) Šulgi , the powerful man , king of Urim , king of Sumer and Akkad : Šūqurtum is his beloved consort ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001717.7",
      "line_range": "7",
      "translation": "(7) Whoever erases this inscription and writes his own name there , may Ninsumun , my personal god , and Lugalbanda , my master , curse him !"
    }
  ],
